longBusinessSummary: China International Development Corporation Limited, an investment holding company, manufactures and distributes leather products in Hong Kong, the United States, Europe, and internationally. The company operates in two segments, Leather Manufacturing Business and Leather Retail Business. It also retails fashion apparel, footwear, and leather accessories. In addition, the company engages in industrial hemp planting; hemp fabric product production; and logistics and warehouse operations businesses. The company operates retail stores under the AREA 0264 name and Teepee leather workshop. China International Development Corporation was incorporated in 2002 and is headquartered in Central, Hong Kong. The company operates as a subsidiary of Waterfront Holding Group Co., Ltd.
